title: Issue in opening a file type after unzipping
content:
I downloaded a file from this link https://storage.cloud.google.com/gresearch/smallcnnzoo-dataset/cifar10.tar.xz, and I successfully downloaded the archive file.I unzipped it using 7-Zip. After unzipping the file format type is file.

I converted it to CSV extension but I am unable to read the data its encoded like below

answers_data.content: Yes, it's obviously not CSV, what made you think it is? You should contact provider of the dataset or use the program that was supplied with it to read it.
